Currently this repository has the following XBMC Addons:
1) IndoLyrics - a lyrics addon script to show hindi lyrics from Giitayan.com, you need a unicode ttf font which is capable of showing hindi characters and the Genre tags of songs should be tagged as hindi.
2) Numi Khoj - search for hindi movies at sites like rangu.com and bharatmovies.com (Note that it uses my modified version of t0mm0's script.module.urlresolver)
